'''丹尼·塞巴洛斯'''（{{lang-es|Dani Ceballos}}，{{IPA-es|ˈdani θeˈβaʎos}}；{{bd|1996年|8月7日}}），是一名[[西班牙|西班牙]]職業足球員，司職[[中場|中場]]，目前效力於[[西甲|西甲]]球會[[皇家馬德里|皇家馬德里]]，亦是[[西班牙國家足球隊|西班牙國家足球隊]]成員之一。

== 球會生涯 ==
=== 貝迪斯 ===
施巴路斯於[[塞維利亞省|塞維利亞省]][[乌特雷拉|乌特雷拉]]出生，2004年，他於8歲時加入[[西維爾足球會|西維爾]]的青訓，但最終於2009年因患上慢性[[支气管炎|支气管炎]]而被球會放棄<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sevilla.eldesmarque.com/real-betis/66971-dani-nike-la-perla-que-brilla-en-el-betis-y-dejo-escapar-el-sevilla|title='Dani Nike', la perla que brilla en el Betis y dejó escapar el Sevilla|trans-title='Dani Nike', the gem who shines in Betis and who Sevilla let slip away|publisher=El Desmarque|last=Aguado|first=Ángel|language=es|date=2014-11-04|accessdate=2014-12-02|archive-date=2017-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703150722/http://sevilla.eldesmarque.com/real-betis/66971-dani-nike-la-perla-que-brilla-en-el-betis-y-dejo-escapar-el-sevilla|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其後，施巴路斯為其家鄉球會CD Utrera上陣，並於2011年被[[皇家贝蒂斯足球俱乐部|贝蒂斯]]簽下<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.alfinaldelapalmera.com/noticias/real-betis/dani-ceballos-las-lagrimas-de-una-madre-por-un-sueno.html|title=Dani Ceballos, las lágrimas de una madre por un sueño|trans-title=Dani Ceballos, the tears of a mother for a dream|newspaper=ABC|last=González|first=M.|language=es|date=2014-04-28|accessdate=2014-05-26|archive-date=2014-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140605022656/http://www.alfinaldelapalmera.com/noticias/real-betis/dani-ceballos-las-lagrimas-de-una-madre-por-un-sueno.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年2月22日，他簽下首份職業合同<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cuentaconlacantera.com/el-betis-ata-una-joya-con-alma-de-entrenador/|title=El Betis ata a una joya con alma de entrenador|trans-title=Betis tie up gem with the soul of a coach|publisher=Cuenta con la Cantera|language=es|date= 2014-02-22|accessdate= 2014-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141207163844/http://www.cuentaconlacantera.com/el-betis-ata-una-joya-con-alma-de-entrenador/|archive-date= 2014-12-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2014年4月26日，施巴路斯未曾為貝迪斯B隊上陣的情況下，被派遣於一線隊上陣。他在主負[[皇家蘇斯達|皇家蘇斯達]]0比1的聯賽中，於比賽尾段後備入替<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.espnfc.com/en/report/372874/report.html?soccernet=true|title= Real Betis 0–1 Real Sociedad|publisher= ESPN FC|date= 2014-04-26|accessdate= 2014-05-26|language= en|archive-date= 2020-04-07|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200407060144/http://www.espnfc.com/en/report/372874/report.html?soccernet=true|dead-url= no}}</ref>。12月21日，施巴路斯於西乙聯賽對陣[[桑坦德競技|桑坦德]]的比賽中，攻入職業生涯首個入球，助球隊於主場以2比0勝出<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.marca.com/2014/12/21/futbol/2adivision/1419167919.html|title=Merino se despide con un pleno y deja al Racing en descenso|trans-title=Merino says goodbye undefeated and leaves Racing inside the relegation zone|newspaper=Marca|language=es|date=2014-12-21|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2017-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170726094326/http://www.marca.com/2014/12/21/futbol/2adivision/1419167919.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。於2014-15賽季，他為球隊上陣33場，攻入5球，協助球隊重返西甲聯賽<ref name=Champions>{{cite news|url=https://elpais.com/deportes/2015/05/25/actualidad/1432550261_534517.html|title=Las siete claves del ascenso del Betis|trans-title=The seven keys of Betis' promotion|newspaper=El País|last=Pineda|first=Rafael|language=es|date=2015-05-25|accessdate=2018-08-21|archive-date=2019-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515164534/https://elpais.com/deportes/2015/05/25/actualidad/1432550261_534517.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

談判了一段長時間後，施巴路斯與貝迪斯續約至2020年<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mundodeportivo.com/futbol/20151015/202223500819/el-betico-dani-ceballos-renueva-hasta-2020.html|title=El bético Dani Ceballos renueva hasta 2020|trans-title=Betis' Dani Ceballos renews until 2020|newspaper=Mundo Deportivo|language=es|date=2015-10-15|accessdate=2016-01-19|archive-date=2017-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816061813/http://www.mundodeportivo.com/futbol/20151015/202223500819/el-betico-dani-ceballos-renueva-hasta-2020.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年4月16日，他於主勝[[埃瓦爾體育協會|-{zh-hans:埃瓦尔;zh-hk:伊巴;zh-tw:埃瓦爾}-]]2比0的聯賽中攻入他在西甲聯賽的首球<ref>{{cite news|url=https://futbol.as.com/futbol/2017/04/16/primera/1492322153_885239.html|title=Joaquín, Adán y Ceballos salvan al Betis y también a Víctor|trans-title=Joaquín, Adán and Ceballos save Betis and Víctor too|newspaper=　Diario AS|last=Espina|first=José A.|language=es|date=2017-04-16|accessdate=2017-08-18|archive-date=2017-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170818091512/https://futbol.as.com/futbol/2017/04/16/primera/1492322153_885239.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 皇家馬德里 ===
2017年7月14日，施巴路斯轉會至[[西班牙甲組足球聯賽|西班牙甲組足球聯賽]]俱樂部[[皇家马德里足球俱乐部|皇家马德里]]，轉會費為1800萬歐元，簽約6年<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.realmadrid.com/noticias/2017/07/comunicado-oficial-dani-ceballos|title= Comunicado oficial: Dani Ceballos|trans-title= Official announcement: Dani Ceballos|publisher= Real Madrid CF|language= es|date= 2017-07-14|accessdate= 2017-07-14|archive-date= 2018-06-22|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180622213353/https://www.realmadrid.com/noticias/2017/07/comunicado-oficial-dani-ceballos|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.marca.com/en/football/real-madrid/2017/07/08/5960b579ca474133128b456d.html|title= Ceballos rejects Barcelona to agree six-year Real Madrid contract|newspaper= Marca|date= 2017-07-08|accessdate= 2017-09-17|language= en|archive-date= 2020-11-09|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201109023820/https://www.marca.com/en/football/real-madrid/2017/07/08/5960b579ca474133128b456d.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。8月16日，他於[[西班牙超級盃|西班牙超級盃]]次回合對陣[[巴塞罗那足球俱乐部|巴塞罗那]]的比賽中，首次代表球會上陣，並以2比0擊敗對手<ref name=TELEGRAPH>{{cite news|url= https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2017/08/16/real-madrid-vs-barcelona-spanish-super-cup-live-score-updates/|title= Real Madrid 2 Barcelona 0 (5–1 on aggregate): Woeful Barca dismissed as Zinedine Zidane's unstoppable side win Super Cup|newspaper= The Daily Telegraph|last= Bull|first= JJ|date= 2017-08-16|accessdate= 2017-08-17|language= en|archive-date= 2018-06-14|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180614021452/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2017/08/16/real-madrid-vs-barcelona-spanish-super-cup-live-score-updates/|dead-url= no}}</ref>。9月23日，施巴路斯於客勝[[阿拉维斯体育|阿拉维斯]]2比1的比賽中首次正選上陣，並[[梅開二度|梅開二度]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.marca.com/eventos/marcador/futbol/2017_18/la-liga/jornada_6/ala_rma/|title=Tomen nota de Ceballos|trans-title=Take note of Ceballos|newspaper=Marca|last=Sánchez|first=Jesús|language=es|date=2017-09-23|accessdate=2017-09-23|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122172553/https://www.marca.com/eventos/marcador/futbol/2017_18/la-liga/jornada_6/ala_rma/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

施巴路斯於[[2017–18年歐洲冠軍聯賽|2017–18年歐洲冠軍聯賽]]中出場4次<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rcnradio.com/deportes/asi-llegan-las-plantillas-de-real-madrid-y-liverpool-la-final-de-la-champions|title=Así llegan Real Madrid y Liverpool a la final de la Champions|trans-title=That is how Real Madrid and Liverpool arrive to the Champions final|publisher=RCN Radio|language=es|date=2018-05-25|accessdate=2018-05-29|archive-date=2018-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615191441/https://www.rcnradio.com/deportes/asi-llegan-las-plantillas-de-real-madrid-y-liverpool-la-final-de-la-champions|dead-url=no}}</ref>，隨隊贏得該屆的冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2018/matches/round=2000885/match=2021711/postmatch/report/index.html|title=Madrid beat Liverpool to complete hat-trick|publisher=UEFA|date=2018-05-26|accessdate=2018-05-28|language=en|archive-date=2019-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330233343/https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2018/matches/round=2000885/match=2021711/postmatch/report/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年1月13日，他於聯賽對陣舊貝迪斯的比賽中，於第74分鐘後備上陣。施巴路斯被貝迪斯的球迷報以噓聲下，於比賽尾段射入[[罰球|罰球]]，最終皇家馬德里以2比1勝出<ref>{{cite news|url= https://www.20minutos.es/deportes/noticia/dani-ceballos-desgraciadamente-gol-betis-real-madrid-3535753/0/|title= Dani Ceballos, tras marcar al Betis: "Desgraciadamente, he metido el gol"|trans-title= Dani Ceballos, after scoring to Betis: "Unfortunately, I scored the goal"|newspaper= 20minutos|language= es|date= 2019-01-13|accessdate= 2019-01-18|archive-date= 2019-04-17|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190417184724/https://www.20minutos.es/deportes/noticia/dani-ceballos-desgraciadamente-gol-betis-real-madrid-3535753/0/|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

=== 阿仙奴（外借）===
2019年7月25日，施巴路斯被外借至[[英格蘭超級足球聯賽|英格蘭超級足球聯賽]]球隊[[阿仙奴足球會|阿仙奴]]，為期一年，將穿上8號球衣<ref>{{cite news|url= https://www.arsenal.com/news/holadani-ceballos-joins-us-loan|title= #HolaDani: Ceballos joins us on loan|publisher= Arsenal F.C. Official Website|date= 2019-07-25|language= en|accessdate= 2019-07-25|archive-date= 2020-09-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200911170805/https://www.arsenal.com/news/holadani-ceballos-joins-us-loan|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.realmadrid.com/en/news/2019/07/official-announcement-ceballos|title=Official Announcement: Ceballos|website=realmadrid.com|date=2019-07-25|language=en|accessdate=2019-07-25|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108022603/https://www.realmadrid.com/en/news/2019/07/official-announcement-ceballos|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月17日，他於對陣[[般尼足球會|般尼]]的聯賽中正選上陣，交出2次助攻，賽後獲得全場最佳球員的獎項<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2019/aug/17/arsenal-burnley-premier-league-match-report|title=Lacazette and Aubameyang give Arsenal the edge over sturdy Burnley|last=Aarons|first=Ed|date=2019-08-17|work=The Observer|access-date=2019-08-17|language=en|issn=0029-7712|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127111505/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2019/aug/17/arsenal-burnley-premier-league-match-report|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月3日，施巴路斯在主勝[[皇家標準列治|標準列治]]4比0的[[2019–20年歐霸盃|欧足联欧洲联赛]]比賽中，射入轉會後首個入球<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/sport/football/arsenal/arsenal-vs-standard-liege-highlights-watch-europa-league-goals-martinelli-willock-ceballos-a4253781.html|title=Arsenal vs Standard Liege highlights: Watch Europa League goals – Martinelli, Willock, Ceballos|last=Doyle|first=Tom|date=2019-10-03|language=en|newspaper=London Evening Standard|access-date=2020-07-19|archive-date=2020-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200719095939/https://www.standard.co.uk/sport/football/arsenal/arsenal-vs-standard-liege-highlights-watch-europa-league-goals-martinelli-willock-ceballos-a4253781.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年6月28日，他於[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]四強對陣[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|谢菲尔德联]]的比賽中，於補時階段射入1球，助球隊晉級四強比賽。2020年8月2日，他於[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]決賽對陣{{fb team 車路士}}的比賽中正選上陣，協助球隊奪得第14個足總盃冠軍。

2020年9月4日，阿仙奴宣佈再次借入塞巴洛斯，繼續穿上8號球衣<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.arsenal.com/news/dani-back-ceballos-returns-loan|title=Dani is back! – Ceballos returns on loan|website=arsenal.com|date=2020-09-04|language=en|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2020-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200914052740/https://www.arsenal.com/news/dani-back-ceballos-returns-loan/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.realmadrid.com/en/news/2020/09/04/official-announcement-ceballos|title=Official Announcement: Ceballos|website=realmadrid.com|date=2020-09-04|accessdate=2020-09-04|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930151507/https://www.realmadrid.com/en/news/2020/09/04/official-announcement-ceballos|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年9月19日，塞巴洛斯在對陣[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|西汉姆]]的比賽中交出助攻，助球隊以2比1勝出<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11670/12076389/arsenal-show-character-against-west-ham-but-creativity-still-lacking|title= Arsenal show character against West Ham but creativity still lacking|date= 2020-09-19|accessdate= 2020-09-20|language= en|work= Skysports|archive-date= 2020-10-30|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201030094700/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11670/12076389/arsenal-show-character-against-west-ham-but-creativity-still-lacking|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

